{"tid":656483,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雙喜臨門！28歲Coffee陀男B三個月秘密入紙","createTime":"2018-05-07T09:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T12:01:34.000Z","uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"98f5a0f0a7fd3046b185ff51ebcb2038d026955d","tid":656483,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:48:21.000Z","msg":"仲做yoga <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180507/large/1525683575_3f85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180507%2Flarge%2F1525683575_3f85.jpg&h=f11554e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n28歲林芊妤(Coffee)今年3月披露同拍拖3年多嘅男友翟志榮有結婚打算，點知今日俾《蘋果》率先發現佢入紙申請結婚，Coffee今日接受《蘋果》訪問表示年初同37歲男友翟志榮有共識，想拉埋天窗，本來打算年尾結婚，但3月尾發現有咗，所以將婚期提前，上周五(4號)秘密入紙。<br />\n<br />\nCoffee一向鍾意小朋友，今次雖然係意外懷孕，但佢同準老公都好開心，佢笑住講：「我父母同埋佢屋企人都好開心，o依家三個幾月，預產期係11月，已經知道係男仔。」問佢同老公係咪鍾意囝囝？Coffee笑言準老公本來鍾意囡囡，不過呢個係天賜嘅小幸運，所以仔女都好開心。<br />\n<br />\n問第一次陀BB有冇好辛苦？Coffee話：「好好彩，冇乜唔舒服，嘔都無乜，不過就係易攰啲。」佢又話o依家仲有教瑜伽，相信自己有專業知識，知道有乜動作可以做，有乜唔可以做，都問晒醫生，所以都安全嘅，而且覺得女人大肚都可以好有power，唔想好似要個個遷就自己咁，所以上堂教學生，都冇人知我大肚。」<br />\n<br />\n問Coffee係咪真係唔會搞婚宴？佢話本來諗住旅行結婚，但有咗BB，可能連旅行都取消，就咁同親友食餐飯就算。問Coffee會唔會停工養胎？Coffee笑言：「唔會，做到BB出世，BB腳頭好呀！好忙，好多嘢做，屋企人都擔心我太勤力，應唔應付到做嘢，怕我好似牛咁做嘢，不過o依家做瑜伽都會自己就住，以前可能出十成力，o依家用一半！」<br />\n<br />\n另外，Coffee今日把聲好似有啲鼻塞，佢話有少少病，因為上個禮拜探完朋友同佢嘅BB後就病咗，醫生話孕婦抵抗力冇咁好，但佢話好彩冇發燒。"},{"pid":"d88edca7ac840c306a04cd6b06eb2a2d2a4d021a","tid":656483,"uid":13718,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"有收陰肌點忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條仔分分鐘腰力都唔洗用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fb8053bcf93223c58bab961f058640edb2e914","tid":656483,"uid":17578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:54:24.000Z","msg":"做開運動先易生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1830f57bd35de907f18a15ffee530995d705aa2a","tid":656483,"uid":9082,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45f646a9ae83f976659db6afccf216f13d3b00e5","tid":656483,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"一定識好多招式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想唔大肚都幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57320a32fca7f2ed10473a5a3d0d5f984e8cd1ae","tid":656483,"uid":35914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d88edca7ac840c306a04cd6b06eb2a2d2a4d021a","tid":656483,"uid":13718,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"有收陰肌點忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條仔分分鐘腰力都唔洗用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:04:52.000Z","msg":"比佢夾到射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7aed3bfd49fe5f08bd7bca1faf96974a4320c9","tid":656483,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:08:31.000Z","msg":"佢條仔就爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw佢之前唔係話帶團去泰國咩"},{"pid":"8e24e0e04bc60496552274b19b1b012d1c288af4","tid":656483,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:09:17.000Z","msg":"好想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937b1ca5ea7ac4d3a03647964082f11c0daee83b","tid":656483,"uid":12254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:35:02.000Z","msg":"人生贏家"},{"pid":"55245006f2b4635ea37ec50e05b00c639441706e","tid":656483,"u